<div class="jumbotron">
    <h1><span class="fa fa-bug"></span> BUGTRACKER</h1>
    <b class="lead">The Bug Tracker is a Web-based software application designed to mirror any of a wide variety of bug tracking software
    systems in use by corporation thoroughout world. If a company develops software, whether for in-house use or distribution, it uses a 
    bug tracking system to maintain an accurate record of the software development process on a per-project basis</b>
    <p/><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bug_tracking_system" target="_blank" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn more &raquo;</a>
</div>
Use one of our easy logins to get a jumpstart on how our BugTracker. You have different roles to chose from. Each having their own individual authority.
<div class="row">
